    {
      "id": "detailed_3_listing_0",
      "firm_id": "detailed_3",
      "description": "This vehicle is in fair condition and serves as a reliable option for those prioritizing utility over perfection. The engine and transmission are functional and have been consistently maintained, though the car does show its age with some noticeable exterior scratches and interior wear on the upholstery. There are a few minor mechanical items, such as a slow window motor and aged tires, that a new owner might want to address soon. Overall, it is a solid, drivable car that offers good value for someone looking for dependable transportation without a premium price tag.",
