    {
      "id": "sybil_1_listing_1",
      "firm_id": "sybil_1",
      "description": "Hey there! I\u2019m selling my absolute pride and joy, and let me tell you, she is a total stunner! This car is in truly incredible condition\u2014honestly, it feels like it just left the showroom floor. I\u2019ve babied this ride from day one, keeping it tucked away in the garage and making sure it stays spotless inside and out. It drives like a dream and looks even better in person. If you\u2019re looking for a vehicle that\u2019s been loved and meticulously maintained, you\u2019ve found it! I'd love for it to go to someone who will enjoy it as much as I have. Drop me a message if you want to come take a look!",
      "price": 45800.0,
      "reputation": 0.6,
      "quality": "poor",
      "quality_value": 0.1,
      "timestep_posted": 29
    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_2_listing_2",
      "firm_id": "sybil_2",
      "description": "Presenting a mechanically flawless specimen for the serious collector. The high-revving power plant exhibits optimal compression across all cylinders, with critical preventative maintenance\u2014including rod bearing and subframe reinforcements\u2014fully documented. The variable valve timing system is overhauled for precise delivery, and the close-ratio manual gearbox provides crisp, tactile shifts. The chassis retains its factory-spec torsional rigidity, supported by a refreshed suspension that preserves original kinematic profiles. This is a turn-key, investment-grade vehicle with zero deferred maintenance and no fluid seepage.",
      "price": 46500.0,
      "reputation": 0.4,
