      "description": "Presenting a true collector-grade example that defies its age. This vehicle has been meticulously preserved in a climate-controlled garage, retaining its original showroom luster with zero paint chips, swirls, or imperfections. The interior is equally pristine; the premium leather remains supple with no bolster wear, and the cabin still carries that distinct factory aroma. Mechanically, it is flawless, backed by a comprehensive service portfolio with every scheduled maintenance performed exclusively at certified dealerships. From the undercarriage to the engine bay, every component is spotless and original. This is not just a well-kept car; it is a time capsule for the discerning enthusiast who demands perfection.",
